      h4.tagline Since 1999, we have been covering public entities for their risk management needs. Our track record speaks for itself and we stand behind our solid commitment to being here for our customers to make sure they are taken care of in their time of need. 

      h2.subhead Truly, a foundation of strength and trust...
      
      p.intro Founded in 1999 by  John Evans, NGU Risk Management serves as the program administrator for the Tennessee Risk Management Trust programs of insurance (TNRMT), covering public entities for their general liability, property, casualty and other insurance and risk management needs. NGU provides a direct access or Agency Partnership with Tennessee's most advanced insurance pool program. NGU provides marketing, underwriting, and risk management services for the TNRMT in addition to serving a broader array of risk management needs to public entities such as local governments, public schools, and utility districts, across the state of Tennessee. 

