      h2.subhead A Message From Betsey
      
      p.intro Thank you for taking a look at NGU and what we have to offer you in serving your risk management needs. Our corporate philosophy emphasizes creativity, innovation, and professionalism with a commitment to serving the public sector's insurance and risk management needs. What makes our perspective unique here at NGU is that we are human beings with families and personal aspirations just like you. We understand risk and have experienced loss in our own lives and working environments, so we know firsthand the pain and frustration that can come with those experiences. But we also know what it takes to make sure you are properly protected in the event of a loss or claim, so you can rest assured that you are taken care of when you're with us. 
      
      p.intro We take our position very seriously, working on behalf of entities that serve the public in making sure that you are properly protected against any liabilities, and fairly treated when a claim is filed. Many of us have served in the public sector, so we know you have enough to worry about watching out for the public good. We make sure that the coverage we create for you is ideally suited to your unique needs and we respect the importance of our relationship with you. NGU offers solutions that simply aren't available anywhere else for the price we can offer them. We know this because our clients tell us. And we are confident that the service we provide to our customers is simply unmatched in the industry. We are proud to say our client retention is high and our rapid growth rate is a testament to our success. 

